<h1>
Storm Preparation with Powermate
</h1>
<p>
With extreme weather events on the rise across the country, you never know what Mother Nature will have in store. Millions of people are left without power each year due to heavy wind and rain that damages power line infrastructures. Power outages can happen when you least expect it, having a large impact on your home and daily routine.

</p>
<p>
This is why Powermate wants to be your storm preparedness partner. We offer a lineup of portable generators that can help you to weather any storm. When you’re prepared with portable power from a Powermate generator, you can be ready at a moment’s notice for outages.

</p>


